data.description: Step into the warmth and comfort of this exquisite 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home, complete with a dedicated office space that could also serve as game room, nestled in the heart of Cross Creek Ranch. Built by Perry Homes, this residence exudes timeless elegance with its no-carpet, showcasing luxurious tile and hardwood flooring throughout. High vaulted ceiling at the entrance hall. Kitchen and baths are adorned with stunning granite countertops, adding a touch of opulence to everyday living. Primary bath offers separate soaking tub and shower. Entertain effortlessly in the spacious open floor interior and unwind on the expansive covered patio, overlooking the charming, low-maintenance backyard. Minutes away from the community gym which faces a lake, cafes, restaurants, day care, pet resort to make your life easier. Zoned to 5 stars Lamar CISD schools with a building for just 6th graders. Don't just buy a house – make this your home.
